cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.RO 

This paper deals with computer vision and image processing techniques for depth recovery using a data-driven approach and deep neural networks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper involves machine learning techniques, which suggests it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves graphics and visualization techniques, which suggests it could belong to cs.GR (Graphics). The use of deep neural networks suggests it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper involves robotics applications, which suggests it could belong to cs.RO (Robotics).
